<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Payment Failure Notification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
    <h2 style="color: #FF5733;">Payment Failed</h2>
    <p>Dear <%= @payment.client.name %>,</p>
    <p>We regret to inform you that your payment for <strong>Dish: <%= @dish.name %></strong> was unsuccessful.</p>

    <h3>Payment Attempt Details:</h3>
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Amount Attempted:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @payment.amount %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Payment Method:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @payment.payment_method %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Transaction ID:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @payment.payment_intent_id %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Date of Attempt:</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= @payment.failed_at %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <p>Unfortunately, the payment could not be processed. Please check your payment details or try again with an alternative method.</p>
    
    <p>If you believe this is an error or need further assistance, please contact our support team.</p>

    <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
